<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 02:10:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>CFTC 为加密货币数万亿美元的离岸贸易铺平道路</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-29/us-paves-way-for-onshore-crypto-linked-perpetual-futures</link><description>多年来，最流行的加密货币交易方式——一种永不过期、被称为永久未来的高杠杆合约——几乎完全超出了美国监管机构的监管范围，在美国法律之外运作的离岸交易所蓬勃发展。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iSltOPwNwg9k/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 14:38:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-29/us-paves-way-for-onshore-crypto-linked-perpetual-futures</guid></item><item><title>SpaceX 炒作刺激了加密货币影子市场的首次公开募股前押注</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-29/spacex-ipo-hype-spurs-crypto-shadow-market-for-pre-listing-bets</link><description>随着 SpaceX 距离历史上最大规模的首次公开募股 (IPO) 越来越近，加密货币市场的一个角落已经在为首次公开募股定价——而最近的历史表明这些数字值得关注。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFGUJQzwUMfI/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 09:15:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-29/spacex-ipo-hype-spurs-crypto-shadow-market-for-pre-listing-bets</guid></item></channel></rss>